title: USA Wrap UP 2003
description:
USA Wrap Up - Allentown PA - Sept. 2002  A condensed version of Dance for Love, with expansion given by the GA during the workshop. Featuring the Eternal Amorea Flame Activations 1-7, Shadow Healing, Identifying Power Nodes, the  "Withness" self-test. Anahazi translation of the last verse of the Psonn of Kehmalohatea, sung by Ashayana Deane. Find out where the safest, safe place on the planet is located and how to create that.

Wormwood, Nibiru, Phantom Matrix, Fourth Battle of Armageddon, Red Pulse, Alcyon - Tara, Polaris - Gaia, The Cradle of Lyra, Crown of Thorns of blockages that has literally stunted the growth of the brain (Crucifixion story), Fireletters, Neutron Window, ManU Window, Silver Sanctum Flame Body, Shadow Bodies, Shadow Dancers, Withness Quiz, Capstone Nodes, Primal Life Force Currents, Apparthi, triggering the Law of Karma, "Nodes" and the "Nodus", Shields, Why Not Suicide, where our thoughts and beliefs come from.
